Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:03.50,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm curious about her... Maybe I'll go have a chat with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:12.00,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:15.51,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.01,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Are you in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.75,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:23.52,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um... well... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:26.52,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for startling you. I'm Utsumi, a student from the Producer Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:32.52,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm Lilja Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:36.27,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for getting startled...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:42.03,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,No, it's my fault for approaching you so suddenly. I just couldn't help but notice you seemed a bit lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:43.87,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.04,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I can't seem to find where the chapel is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:53.55,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Would you like me to walk with you part of the way? I'm headed in that direction too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:54.32,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:59.55,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um... that would be really helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:02.75,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Could I ask you for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:09.06,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Oh, so you just arrived in Japan, Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:10.06,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:15.22,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I came over here when I enrolled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:19.07,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm surprised. Your Japanese is really natural for someone who just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:21.89,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,My father is Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:28.23,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,And I've been learning from my Japanese friend, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:32.96,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Will I really be able to communicate properly at a Japanese school?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:36.31,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I was really worried about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:41.09,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hearing that from you, Senpai, makes me feel a bit more at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:43.49,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:50.77,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You call someone older who attends the same school "Senpai," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:52.32,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.97,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:58.61,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Did I make a mistake with my Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:00.78,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,No, there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:05.62,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,May I ask you something? Why did you choose to come to this academy, Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:09.39,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,My friend invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:13.41,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She said we should become idols together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:18.63,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She said, "Let's go to an idol school so we can become idols."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:23.28,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm... not very confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:26.39,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,At first, I thought about turning it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:29.14,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Was there something that changed your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:32.01,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I watched a live performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:35.53,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,At this academy. Together with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.65,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.15,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It was really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:42.45,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It was truly incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.66,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:47.66,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:51.85,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,"I want to be like that too."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:55.46,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's how I've come to feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:58.97,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Of course, it's presumptuous of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:04.05,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm clumsy, and I'm not cute either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.18,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:07.18,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:09.18,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,No matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.18,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want to become an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:16.69,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...You have a good look in your eyes. I'm sure you can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:19.19,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:23.70,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Lilja, what do you think is the most important talent for an idol to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:24.50,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.48,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:33.71,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Being cute, or being good at singing and dancing, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:39.06,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's very important, but it's not the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:41.71,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's... difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:47.61,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Being able to speak well, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:52.22,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,The most important talent for an idol isn't that. The most crucial talent is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:54.73,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Having a strong will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.98,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,The talent to have courage and take a step towards your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.73,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:03.88,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I... I don't have any courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.24,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You do have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:10.49,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You decided to become an idol and convinced your parents, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:12.86,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:17.61,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You studied hard, took the exams, passed, and left your family to come to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:23.10,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,This is a foreign land. It's natural to feel anxious. You might not even be sure if you'll be understood properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:26.01,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,But here you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:29.76,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I really want to become one, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:34.95,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That day, I dreamed of becoming an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.27,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...And here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:41.98,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I originally just intended to have a chat, but... I've changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.28,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.28,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.49,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Please allow me to be your producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:51.78,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What? ...No way!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:55.29,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,M-me...? Are you serious...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:05:00.53,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Absolutely. Let's aim even higher than just admiration. Let's strive to become a top idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:07.30,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.30,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:13.01,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:16.51,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um, please—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:19.51,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.15,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I ended up scouting her on impulse... but I'm sure she'll become a wonderful idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:28.82,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:32.32,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to working with you starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:34.83,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes, let's work hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.83,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:41.33,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:45.09,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see your enthusiasm. Let's start by talking about your lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.53,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.95,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So, what should I do first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.85,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What do you think I should do instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.56,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.14,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Everything...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.71,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Well, to put it simply, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:06.70,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,But there's no need to worry. You're a complete beginner, right, Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.36,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:12.66,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I've never had any experience with singing or dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:16.25,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I don't even know how to approach the lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.62,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even if I throw myself into the lessons,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.37,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I don't really feel like it's making much of a difference...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:25.71,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,The producer's job is to help with those kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:29.38,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I've come up with a lesson plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:29.38,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,So, where should we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.55,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You're talking about the lessons, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.89,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:39.89,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Alright, let's focus on strengthening your singing first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:42.30,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Singing, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:45.05,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So, vocal lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:49.90,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes. Trying to do everything at once from the start will just lead to confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:50.90,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:54.78,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's how I've been up until now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:58.91,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Everything just ends up being half-baked...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:03.59,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's take it one step at a time and move forward steadily. Today, we'll start with vocal exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.27,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:08.09,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You're really dependable, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.72,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Well, I am a producer, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.93,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.17,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Having someone I can rely on is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.78,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Relieving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:22.67,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I just arrived in Japan, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:26.70,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I don't have many friends, so I feel a bit lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:30.44,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I do have one close friend, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.94,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I've been relying too much on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:37.45,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,From now on, I'll be here with you. If anything comes up, feel free to rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.61,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:43.46,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.21,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you for choosing someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:49.66,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want to live up to your expectations, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:53.22,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,And so, I'll become an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:56.97,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Lilja, could you say that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.28,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll become an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.97,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Louder, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:04.75,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,W-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.82,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:12.48,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be embarrassed about. No one at this school will laugh at that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:17.78,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:22.81,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,So, declare it with confidence. Speak loudly and clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:25.38,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Y-yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:29.00,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I will become an idol...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:33.51,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Your voice is still a bit quiet. Try to imagine projecting it from your diaphragm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:40.27,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's already night, isn't it? Let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:44.02,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huff, huff...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:47.52,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,My stomach... it kind of hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:52.02,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Ah, it's muscle soreness. You use your muscles for diaphragmatic breathing, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:57.03,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But... but... I can still keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:09:00.88,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Really? You already look exhausted, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:05.77,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,For someone like me to become an idol, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:09.04,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I can't just be like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:13.22,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I need to put in more time and effort than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:16.87,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Alright. If you can say that, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:21.55,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,But let's take a short break. There's no point in pushing yourself to the point of exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:24.56,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Haa, haa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.56,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:31.06,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's great that you're so motivated. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:35.44,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, Senpai, I was able to have a really great lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:38.57,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I'm still lacking in skills, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:42.57,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I feel like I've grown just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:46.62,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I've felt this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.08,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's why I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:54.59,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,If you feel like you've grown, that's the result of your hard work, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:58.09,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,All I can do as the Producer is lend a helping hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.59,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:03.19,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I hope you don't feel too accomplished just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:07.71,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Lilja, you still have so much room to grow. Today is just the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.10,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Is that really the case...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:14.81,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'll pave the way for you to become an idol. All you need to do, Katsuragi, is keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.11,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.29,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Can someone like me really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:22.11,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Can I really become one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.81,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You can do it, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:28.12,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I will make you an idol. Please believe in my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.62,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:31.86,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.63,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I keep saying negative things—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:37.79,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I, I will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:41.27,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I will become an idol!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:45.64,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...! You've got great volume. It looks like today's vocal practice really paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:48.64,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hehe... I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.64,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:58.15,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's make a note of today's production status.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:02.15,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Her enthusiasm and determination is impressive. Let's keep this up and gradually build her skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.86,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,How did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:20.67,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Your vocal exercises have really helped stabilize your volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:23.17,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hehe... I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.48,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:29.18,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um... Is there something that's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:33.58,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Hmm, well, it's a bit tricky to say right now, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:37.02,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I've noticed your expression is a bit stiff, and it's been on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:39.19,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Expression, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:44.20,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Alright. Katsuragi, what kind of expression did the idol you like have on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:49.20,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She was smiling and looked like she was having so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.71,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She looked like she was having such a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:57.21,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I felt happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.71,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I felt energized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:03.85,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn, Katsuragi, to bring energy to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.86,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Okay, got it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:10.54,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's great that you're serious about your lessons, but how about practicing your expressions for the real performance as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:15.01,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Specifically, try to smile more. Even while you're singing, make a conscious effort to keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:18.01,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,A smile, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:20.14,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I feel kind of embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:24.24,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Have confidence. Your smile is really cute, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.06,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,C-cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:32.63,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,M-me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.10,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.11,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.43,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,H-huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:44.15,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,This isn't really a smile, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:48.26,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's perfect. A genuine smile is always best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.50,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.76,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Because it made me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:56.88,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I know it might be difficult, but your expression is part of the performance too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:00.27,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi, I'me sure a gentle expression suits you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:03.27,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm not confident, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:09.03,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But I want to get closer to that sparkling smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.28,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.01,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Alright, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:13.79,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,—Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:14.97,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:17.93,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,L-like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:22.29,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,What exactly is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:25.29,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:29.17,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I was trying to smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:32.30,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Could you try to make it look a bit more natural?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:34.56,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:37.53,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Did I really look that bad...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:42.13,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's not that, but you were trying too hard and ended up making a funny face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:46.21,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's try to smile more naturally. Just relax, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:50.18,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Y-yes. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:56.33,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,L-like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:01.33,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't believe you're laughing, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:05.34,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh? Did I mess something up...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:09.07,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's just that your expression was a bit amusing... hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:13.01,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,In a way, it seems like you have a talent for uplifting everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:18.35,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,No, I think you're heading in the wrong direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:21.15,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,No, but... that face you made earlier... haha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:24.16,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Please, don't laugh so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:25.86,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll start laughing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.60,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's a much better smile than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:36.59,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Well, it's because you were laughing so much, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:39.99,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But somehow, I think I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:44.22,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,A natural, genuine smile is good enough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:46.29,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:47.99,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,In front of the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:51.25,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Right... making the face you did just now in front of a mirror might actually be good practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.09,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:00.62,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,No, no! It's nothing. Ahem, ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.14,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Um, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:06.14,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's work hard on our practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:10.69,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,On stage, in front of a large audience, to be able to inspire and energize everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.62,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Got it…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.23,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's make a note of today's production status.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:23.92,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Her smile will be a great asset. Let's keep refining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.42,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(...She's improving.)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:35.25,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(Even if she's taking it one step at a time)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:44.44,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I've finished the lesson menu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:47.83,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Great job. Take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:50.63,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Your expression has softened a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.05,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Really? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:56.35,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm glad I've been practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:59.95,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Oh, I'm a bit thirsty, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.67,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll go buy a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:04.30,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.65,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Lilja's taking a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.80,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'll go check on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:15.14,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Senpai is a really good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:19.12,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,He's kind, knowledgeable, and capable of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.47,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,He's really guiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:23.79,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(Oh, she's talking with her friends.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:27.84,Default,アイドル科の生徒A,0,0,0,,Wow, that's nice. I wish I had a Producer too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:31.12,Default,アイドル科の生徒B,0,0,0,,I know, right? I'm really jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:35.21,Default,アイドル科の生徒B,0,0,0,,But it's strange, isn't it? Why Lilja, of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:36.29,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:39.65,Default,アイドル科の生徒B,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I didn't mean it in a bad way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:43.49,Default,アイドル科の生徒B,0,0,0,,You know, there are plenty of other good students around, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:46.62,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:50.34,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm not doing well in my classes either...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:54.74,Default,アイドル科の生徒B,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it like that. I'm just wondering why it had to be Lilja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:59.01,Default,アイドル科の生徒A,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is a bit strange, isn't it? I mean, I don't want to sound rude, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:03.76,Default,アイドル科の生徒A,0,0,0,,It's not like you're particularly good at singing or dancing, and you don't really stand out appearance-wise either...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:09.29,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:12.52,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Because I saw something special in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:16.75,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,When it comes to producing idols, no other reason is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.87,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:22.53,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't mean to eavesdrop, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:26.54,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I overheard some not-so-great comments about the idol I'm working with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:29.04,Default,アイドル科の生徒A,0,0,0,,Oh, no, that's not what I meant... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.40,Default,アイドル科の生徒B,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:34.55,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I believe Katsuragi can become a top idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:38.77,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's why I'm producing you. ...Let's go, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:41.05,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:42.55,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.22,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm going...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:51.34,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I got a bit carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:54.18,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...No, I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:57.71,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You were protecting me, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:18:01.57,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's just how I really feel. ...Are you okay, Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.34,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.58,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I already knew without anyone else having to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:09.34,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I don't have any talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:10.75,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:14.47,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But that's just a given.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:17.59,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's not a reason to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.31,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:23.89,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:28.88,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even so, I want to believe in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:32.60,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So let's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:35.50,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I can still keep pushing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:40.29,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...It's because you can say things like that, Katsuragi, that I decided to produce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:45.12,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You may not have any standout talents. But that's your one, your only—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.49,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,—and greatest weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:51.39,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...It might not be my only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:53.62,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Up until now, just having that was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:57.63,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Now I have you by my side, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:01.97,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Thanks to that, I can work harder than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.63,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Lilja...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:06.36,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm going to become an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:11.14,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Being a top idol... that's a bit much for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.75,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm not that confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:17.65,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Try to play it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:17.65,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Well then, just aim to be a regular idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:21.15,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Uh... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:24.15,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I think I'll try to be a top idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:27.66,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Well said. Let's continue with the lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:31.85,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,To become a top idol, we'll push hard. Really hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:37.17,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Eek...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:40.40,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,The Producer seems a bit intimidating...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.67,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But, but I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:47.68,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Please be tough on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:54.32,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's reorganize the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:59.19,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Her passion and determination to become an idol are genuine. I'm sure she'll keep getting better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.69,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hello, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:05.95,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you for your support today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.70,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Hello, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:11.20,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Starting today, we'll gradually move into more practical lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:13.95,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:18.21,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Up until now, we've focused almost exclusively on vocal lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:22.21,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,We've only done the bare minimum to address weaknesses, like practicing facial expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.51,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:33.22,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Basically, it's been about vocal exercises, breathing techniques, pronunciation, pitch control, and rhythm strengthening—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:36.23,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,After that, it's just singing over and over, correcting as I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.91,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I've been doing a lot of practical training.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:42.95,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes. It's steady progress, but you're growing little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:46.10,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Am I getting any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.65,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I don't really feel it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:53.94,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's okay. If you're feeling unsure, would you like to watch some of the early recordings?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.25,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Recordings, you say...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:21:00.25,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes. We always keep a record of our daily lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:04.98,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Ah, here it is. This is the recording from your first day of lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.01,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,―This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.37,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Not great, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:13.26,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I can barely hear my voice at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.99,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,And I couldn't maintain pitch either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:16.77,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,The rhythm too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:21.11,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Alright, let me show you the next recording. This is from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.27,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:25.28,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh, what's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:27.28,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:33.28,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I think I might be getting a little better, at least for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:37.01,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes. You're growing, Lilja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:39.67,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It seems like it, doesn't it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:44.30,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Seeing this, I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:47.60,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...But I still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:51.30,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Of course, that's exactly right. There's still plenty of room for growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:55.81,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's not a skill that improves overnight. Let's build it up steadily, step by step.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:57.93,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Y-yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:22:01.99,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Starting today, let's focus more on the fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:06.47,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You're going to gain what you need to stand on that stage, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:09.23,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What am I missing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:13.32,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Imagine yourself standing on that stage right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.32,0:22:16.50,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Me, on stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:21.54,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,A large audience is watching. They're eagerly anticipating your performance, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:25.84,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Just like you did, with eyes sparkling...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:31.55,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,They're all here... just to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:35.85,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Your hands are shaking. You're not comfortable in front of people, are you, Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:38.35,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:41.35,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm not really good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:45.98,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I'm aiming to become an idol, so I can't let this hold me back, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:50.36,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But it's not that I dislike it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:53.57,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I just get so nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:22:58.09,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Being nervous isn't a bad thing. It just shows how serious you are about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:23:02.65,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,What you're missing, Katsuragi, is experience — specifically, experience performing in front of an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:07.99,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:12.19,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You mean practicing performing in front of people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.19,0:23:16.39,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Exactly. Little by little, you'll get used to being in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:22.09,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Do you think it might be a bother to have them practice with someone like me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:25.90,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll call over some students from the Idol Course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:30.00,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Watching and learning is also part of the lesson. I'm sure they'll be willing to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:32.27,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh... I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:40.59,Default,アイドル科の生徒A,0,0,0,,Huh, there's no one here. Even though class has already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:43.56,Default,アイドル科の生徒B,0,0,0,,Seriously. I wonder what that's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:47.38,Default,アイドル科の生徒C,0,0,0,,Today's lesson is all about learning by watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:51.83,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Eek...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:54.43,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,There are more people than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:57.24,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I can't do it, Senpai... It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:24:00.93,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Compared to the actual performance, this is a much smaller crowd, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:05.16,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Y-yeah... I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.16,0:24:09.10,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Just relax. Just sing like you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.10,0:24:11.15,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Y-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.61,0:24:13.92,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Just like always, just like always...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.15,0:24:17.37,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Remember, this is just a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.15,0:24:17.37,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Think of this as the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.69,0:24:21.59,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Th-this is the real thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.59,0:24:24.38,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Uh, oh no no no...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.38,0:24:27.96,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(I don't expect her to get it right from the start.)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.96,0:24:31.64,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(What's important is developing an awareness for the real performance.)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.37,0:24:37.09,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm Lilja Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.09,0:24:38.54,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll sing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.47,0:24:44.53,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.53,0:24:48.07,Default,アイドル科の生徒A,0,0,0,,Don't get too down about it. It's normal for a first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.07,0:24:51.32,Default,アイドル科の生徒B,0,0,0,,Try to relax a bit more. You've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.32,0:24:55.39,Default,アイドル科の生徒C,0,0,0,,It feels kind of nostalgic, doesn't it? We learned a lot too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.39,0:24:57.81,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.76,0:25:02.92,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Great job today. You really worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.92,0:25:06.37,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...But it was a complete disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.37,0:25:12.44,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even after all that practice, my voice was shaking, and I couldn't sing well at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.44,0:25:19.08,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,If I perform like this in the real thing... I'll just end up disappointing everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.08,0:25:22.77,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,If things stay as they are now, yes. But only if things stay as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.77,0:25:28.11,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's just like before. It's okay to take it step by step and gradually improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.11,0:25:31.55,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You can do it. I believe in you, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.55,0:25:33.77,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.77,0:25:36.77,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.77,0:25:39.79,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you for believing in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.79,0:25:44.54,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, Senpai, I've realized so many of my weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.54,0:25:48.23,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I believe that you can overcome this, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.23,0:25:51.84,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll face myself, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.22,0:25:56.89,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So this time, I'll make sure to—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.89,0:26:00.40,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll be able to sing in front of everyone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.55,0:26:06.87,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'll make a note of today's production status.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.87,0:26:11.06,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Overcoming stage fright is absolutely essential. Now, how should we proceed...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.33,0:26:22.75,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.75,0:26:26.82,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(She's gradually improving. Now it's just a matter of being concious of it.)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.85,0:26:30.58,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.58,0:26:33.34,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it well again today...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.34,0:26:36.59,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Lilja, let's talk about something fundamental for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.59,0:26:39.66,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Something fundemental...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.97,0:26:43.05,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.05,0:26:47.29,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I believe that being an idol is a profession where you let people see who you truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.29,0:26:51.29,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,By showing your shining self, you captivate people and inspire them to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.60,0:26:54.31,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.53,0:26:58.07,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...So that's what being an idol is all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.07,0:27:02.15,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,But right now, Katsuragi, you're afraid to show your true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.43,0:27:04.09,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.09,0:27:05.87,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.87,0:27:08.40,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Because I lack confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.01,0:27:12.48,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,In myself, and in my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.48,0:27:17.42,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I just can't believe that someone like me could move people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.42,0:27:22.04,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's why you get so tense and close yourself off, hoping no one will notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.04,0:27:24.28,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.28,0:27:27.31,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's okay to not be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.80,0:27:28.53,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.53,0:27:32.38,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Of course, it's always better to do things well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.38,0:27:35.19,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.19,0:27:38.81,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,But technique isn't everything. What really matters is the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.81,0:27:42.39,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,During the last lesson, were you thinking about the audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.93,0:27:47.31,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I was just trying to do it well earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.92,0:27:50.31,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I was just focused on trying to do it well...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.32,0:27:53.16,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,The people who were watching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.16,0:27:55.67,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,…I wasn't thinking about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.67,0:27:59.88,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's true that technique is important. But technique alone won't reach people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.88,0:28:04.35,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,What matters most is the intention to connect with others. Show them the best of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.35,0:28:05.82,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.45,0:28:09.99,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm so nervous that I can't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.99,0:28:12.48,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Giving it my all and doing my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.29,0:28:16.76,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That was the only thing I had going for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.76,0:28:23.02,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I was truly drawn to your strong will, unbreakable spirit, and earnest dedication, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.02,0:28:28.49,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Even if your skills are still developing, Katsuragi, your performance will surely touch people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.49,0:28:30.76,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.76,0:28:32.87,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.35,0:28:35.66,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I feel like I've woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.66,0:28:37.39,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,The person I am now,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.21,0:28:42.65,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll show the audience everything I've got right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.65,0:28:47.53,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,With everything I have, I'll move people's hearts...!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.53,0:28:51.06,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's the spirit. I'm sure you can do it, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.06,0:28:54.75,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's continue with the same lessons starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.75,0:28:56.50,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.63,0:29:00.96,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I have a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.96,0:29:04.06,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,What is it? It's rare to get a suggestion from you, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.06,0:29:06.34,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,For the next lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.85,0:29:09.11,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Can I invite a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.11,0:29:12.24,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Of course, that's fine, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.24,0:29:15.75,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...She's my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.05,0:29:20.58,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,To me, she's one of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.58,0:29:25.51,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want Sumika to see who I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.51,0:29:28.43,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want to reach her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.37,0:29:32.57,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She's someone I truly feel that way about.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.57,0:29:36.51,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,So, you want to show her first, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.51,0:29:37.46,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.27,0:29:42.59,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I thought this might help overcome my fear of being in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.59,0:29:44.08,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.08,0:29:48.44,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,As your Producer, I want to respect your wishes as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.44,0:29:51.47,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you so much...!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.47,0:29:54.28,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It will definitely reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.10,0:29:59.79,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,The person I am now will reach her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.79,0:30:06.10,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'll make a note of today's production progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.10,0:30:10.11,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm sure that with the person Lilja is now, she'll be able to reach her best friend's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.23,0:30:13.53,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Is this the right place?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.93,0:30:16.93,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,This is such a weird lesson, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.93,0:30:19.43,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Just watching someone else's lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.43,0:30:22.97,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Welcome, Sumika Shiun. I've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.97,0:30:27.74,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Hi there! Are you the person from the Producer Course who invited me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.74,0:30:31.43,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm the Producer. Please, come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.36,0:30:35.67,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, Sumika!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.67,0:30:38.23,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,What, Lilja!?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.23,0:30:40.92,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Is today's lesson going to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.92,0:30:42.33,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.95,0:30:44.69,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm going to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.69,0:30:47.43,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm really looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.43,0:30:49.58,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,You've been working really hard lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.58,0:30:50.84,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.34,0:30:54.20,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Because I want to become an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.20,0:30:57.85,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.34,0:31:02.84,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm still not as good as you, Sumika, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.84,0:31:06.71,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want you to see who I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.71,0:31:09.25,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I asked Senpai for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.25,0:31:11.65,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Lilja?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.65,0:31:14.44,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,You shouldn't compare yourself to someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.44,0:31:20.87,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Sumika, are you really not interested in becoming an idol anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.87,0:31:27.29,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Hmm, it's not that I'm not interested, but it might be a bit difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.29,0:31:31.01,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Oh, but my love for idols hasn't changed at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.01,0:31:33.49,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'm cheering for you too, Lilja!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.49,0:31:35.29,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'll be here to support you as a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.29,0:31:39.60,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'm really looking forward to today's lesson if Lilja is going to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.39,0:31:42.89,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.89,0:31:44.99,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Watch me, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.99,0:31:48.07,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Alright, Katsuragi, please get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.07,0:31:49.69,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.31,0:31:57.65,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Have you given up on becoming an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.65,0:32:00.72,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,...Did you hear what we were talking about earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.72,0:32:03.05,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I didn't say that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.05,0:32:08.26,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,But you know, becoming an idol isn't something that happens easily, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.26,0:32:10.30,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'm not really serious about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.30,0:32:13.30,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,And I can't get as into it as Lilja has.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.30,0:32:17.82,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,That's kind of what I'm thinking, but am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.82,0:32:20.93,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,...No, I don't think so. Everyone has their own way of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.81,0:32:26.13,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,My friend invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.13,0:32:30.20,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,We decided to become idols together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.03,0:32:35.50,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...She's my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.77,0:32:40.29,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,To me, she's one of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.29,0:32:45.23,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want Sumika to see who I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.23,0:32:48.23,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want to reach her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.96,0:32:52.17,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She's someone I truly feel that way about.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.12,0:32:59.34,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Listening to her sing is nice and all, but what exactly is this lesson supposed to be about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.34,0:33:03.90,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Lilja struggles with being in front of people, so she's training to overcome that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.90,0:33:06.90,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Oh, right, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.90,0:33:09.60,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Lilja gets pretty nervous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.60,0:33:13.29,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Lilja said she wanted you to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.29,0:33:16.53,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She wants to show you the person she's become.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.53,0:33:20.26,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.99,0:33:24.34,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,She doesn't have to go through all the trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.34,0:33:28.16,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I already know she's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.16,0:33:33.44,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right. Katsuragi is truly amazing. I can really feel it as her producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.44,0:33:37.93,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Please stay and watch Katsuragi's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.93,0:33:43.62,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Hmm, if you're going to say that much, I guess I'll have to look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.62,0:33:46.13,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.02,0:33:50.52,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Can I start right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.52,0:33:53.18,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Alright. Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.18,0:33:54.52,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.30,0:33:57.89,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Watch me, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.90,0:34:02.46,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Lilja Katsuragi... I'm going to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.75,0:34:15.55,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hah, hah...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.55,0:34:18.19,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So, how was it, Sumika...?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.19,0:34:22.05,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Wow! That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.05,0:34:25.06,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,That's the Lilja I believed in!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.06,0:34:28.95,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Lilja, your performance just now was fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.95,0:34:34.06,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Really? I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.56,0:34:37.63,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I actually sang it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.63,0:34:41.83,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I've gained a little bit of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.83,0:34:44.83,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you and Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.83,0:34:49.22,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's good to hear. However, there were a few mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.22,0:34:53.58,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Uh... y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.58,0:34:55.99,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I know that myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.99,0:35:01.47,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll practice where I made mistakes, and next time, I'll sing even better...!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.47,0:35:04.47,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.07,0:35:09.10,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,You're really giving it your all!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.10,0:35:11.98,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,It's like you're a completely different person from just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.98,0:35:14.99,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm still inexperienced, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.99,0:35:17.99,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to  Senpai for guiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.99,0:35:20.61,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,…I may not have talent, but
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.61,0:35:23.61,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,He gave me the push I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.61,0:35:27.07,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I can move forward little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.81,0:35:29.28,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.62,0:35:31.49,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'm really glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.86,0:35:34.28,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,You found a good producer, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.28,0:35:39.02,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Lilja's really shining right now, even just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.33,0:35:42.13,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.13,0:35:45.14,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.14,0:35:47.45,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thanks to Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.45,0:35:50.45,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I feel like I've changed a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.75,0:35:55.50,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I realized that what's important is the desire to reach out and connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.50,0:35:59.76,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Until yesterday, Katsuragi seemed to shrink under the audience's gaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.76,0:36:04.00,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,If this lesson helped you find a way to overcome your challenges, that's the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.00,0:36:06.16,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.16,0:36:08.38,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I think I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.38,0:36:10.66,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.66,0:36:13.25,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'm glad I could be of help to Lilja.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.25,0:36:15.99,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,If anything comes up, just let me know, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.99,0:36:19.24,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'm free, so I'm always here to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.24,0:36:24.73,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Hehe, when Lilja becomes an idol, I'm going to brag about being one of her original fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.73,0:36:32.18,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Sumika, I haven't given up on our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.18,0:36:35.44,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,...What promise was that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.69,0:36:38.93,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I forget things so easily, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.93,0:36:43.48,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,...Well, I guess it's time for me to head out!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.48,0:36:45.45,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I've got a friend calling me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.45,0:36:47.47,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Good luck, Lilja!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.47,0:36:50.20,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,See you later, Producer!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.14,0:36:54.43,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.60,0:36:58.12,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Shall we get back to the lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.60,0:36:58.12,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.35,0:37:00.71,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.94,0:37:02.50,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.09,0:37:06.57,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I believe in Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.57,0:37:11.90,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Sumika's talent and mine... they're just not comparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.90,0:37:16.55,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Until Sumika gets back, I need to catch up, even just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.55,0:37:20.62,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Yes, that's right. Let's make sure you can keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.62,0:37:22.44,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.49,0:37:29.60,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's make a note of today's production status.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.60,0:37:33.58,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,For now, she's taken a step forward. I'm sure her relationship with her best friend will too...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.69,0:37:37.25,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Lilja, I've got some good news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.25,0:37:38.49,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.25,0:37:40.56,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.56,0:37:44.80,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,The date for the live performance has been set. It's going to be your first live show, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.80,0:37:45.88,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.88,0:37:48.57,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You look completely taken aback.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.57,0:37:54.76,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,W-wait, a live show...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.76,0:37:58.41,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Isn't it too soon for me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.41,0:38:02.21,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's true that up until now, we've focused on the basics...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.21,0:38:07.62,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Based on your progress, Katsuragi, I've decided it's time for you to move on to the next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.62,0:38:12.06,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,A l-live, me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.06,0:38:15.04,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry so much; you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.04,0:38:19.79,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Idol course students grow by experiencing live performances repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.79,0:38:26.55,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,A l-live performance... me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.55,0:38:27.84,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.84,0:38:29.67,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Y-yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.67,0:38:32.14,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I-I-I-I'll do my best...!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.14,0:38:34.41,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.41,0:38:36.45,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm just so nervous, it's getting to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.45,0:38:39.53,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Please calm down. It's still a ways off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.53,0:38:42.09,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But, still...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.09,0:38:46.46,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You've gotten to the point where you can sing confidently in front of others. You'll be just fine, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.46,0:38:50.13,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself. You can do it, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.13,0:38:53.23,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.23,0:38:57.97,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Alright, shall we start the lesson? From today, we'll gradually incorporate some dance as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.97,0:39:01.33,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,A live performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.04,0:39:09.18,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,—Four hours after the lesson ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.18,0:39:13.10,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I can't believe I left my house keys at school... How careless of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.10,0:39:17.12,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Hmm? The lights are still on... Is someone still in the practice room?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.12,0:39:24.35,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Hah, Hah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.37,0:39:31.86,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,This isn't good enough... This just won't do...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.86,0:39:37.73,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Better, better, I need to get even better...!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.73,0:39:42.93,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hah, Hah... Cough, cough!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.09,0:39:47.62,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I need to energize everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.62,0:39:50.67,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I need to give a great performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.67,0:39:56.13,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll deliver my song to everyone's hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.13,0:39:57.39,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.39,0:40:01.13,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Oh, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.13,0:40:03.48,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Wh-why are you here so late...?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.48,0:40:07.87,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's what I should be saying to you. Have you really been practicing all this time since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.87,0:40:11.23,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I just couldn't sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.23,0:40:14.28,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I won't make it as I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.28,0:40:17.23,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I need to try harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.91,0:40:20.23,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh, what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.23,0:40:23.17,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,—Katsuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.42,0:40:27.42,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.42,0:40:30.04,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm feeling a bit unsteady on my feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.04,0:40:33.01,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Katsuragi. Let's call it a day and head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.01,0:40:37.40,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's true that hard work is important. But overworking yourself will only harm your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.40,0:40:40.93,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But as I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.93,0:40:44.48,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm still not good enough at singing or dancing...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.48,0:40:47.85,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Are you really that scared? Of your first live performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.34,0:40:52.83,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...My body just starts trembling on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.83,0:40:56.45,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm just not there yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.64,0:41:00.81,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I think it's too soon for a live performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.81,0:41:02.38,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Alright, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.38,0:41:06.86,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's just call it a day and head home. How about taking a break tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.86,0:41:09.86,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.46,0:41:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,—The next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.69,0:41:18.48,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai, what brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.48,0:41:21.43,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I told you, we're taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.43,0:41:26.57,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're actually taking a break, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.57,0:41:31.61,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Usually, it's all about lessons, lessons, and more lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.61,0:41:34.01,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Is that really the impression you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.01,0:41:38.23,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Maybe I should have been a bit kinder to Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.23,0:41:41.92,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Oh, it's almost time. Let's hurry, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.33,0:41:45.20,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.20,0:41:48.76,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You'll find out soon enough. I've already got the tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.14,0:41:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- The concert venue
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.83,0:41:55.38,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Wow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.38,0:42:00.32,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,For people like us, I thought this would be the best way to unwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.71,0:42:03.32,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.32,0:42:05.71,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've been to a live show.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.71,0:42:10.33,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,The ones who were just on stage are all students from the Idol Course.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.33,0:42:15.98,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,They were so confident up there, and yet they're students just like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.98,0:42:19.94,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,This is part of your learning too. Let's observe and learn from how they carry themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.94,0:42:21.03,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.23,0:42:26.29,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Isn't today supposed to be a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.41,0:42:29.36,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.41,0:42:29.36,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Of course, I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.75,0:42:32.94,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I didn't know you could joke around, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.94,0:42:35.04,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's unusual and refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.04,0:42:39.41,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You wouldn't want to forget that enjoying the performance is what's most important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.41,0:42:43.98,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I thought it would be a good idea for you to reaffirm the place you're aiming for, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.98,0:42:45.65,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.65,0:42:48.88,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,How did you feel watching those idols?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.88,0:42:53.06,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,They're really amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.06,0:42:57.69,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Everyone's so dazzling and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.69,0:43:01.35,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Next time, it'll be you, Katsuragi, standing on that stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.70,0:43:06.08,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Doesn't it make you excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.70,0:43:06.08,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll be a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.68,0:43:09.58,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes, it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.70,0:43:14.49,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want to stand there as soon as possible, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.49,0:43:17.59,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.49,0:43:22.00,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes, truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.00,0:43:28.44,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I remembered the reason why I first wanted to become an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.44,0:43:31.60,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Watching the school live performance with Sumika...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.10,0:43:34.71,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I just admired it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.71,0:43:37.99,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want to stand on that stage too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.93,0:43:42.55,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want to sing and dance to lift everyone's spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.55,0:43:44.97,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You can do it, Katsuragi, with the way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.97,0:43:49.48,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I understand you're nervous. But there's no need to be scared or intimidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.48,0:43:51.03,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.03,0:43:54.85,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy it. After all, it's your first live performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.85,0:43:59.15,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Enjoy it... Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.15,0:44:02.31,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,This is the place I've been aiming for.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.31,0:44:07.33,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Alright... Once the live performance is over, I need to get back to practicing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.33,0:44:11.02,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's not a good idea. Take it easy and rest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.02,0:44:13.55,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.55,0:44:17.84,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,No need to look so defeated. We'll get back to our rigorous schedule starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.84,0:44:20.90,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.90,0:44:24.09,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm so happy, thank you so much...!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.09,0:44:27.88,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to make our first live show a success...!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.66,0:44:35.77,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's go over the report again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.77,0:44:39.76,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,With the Lilja Katsuragi we have now, I'm sure she'll be just fine. I hope she enjoys the live show.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.83,0:44:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,—The day of the first live show.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.42,0:44:47.52,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,The day has finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.52,0:44:54.48,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Wow... I can't believe there are so many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.48,0:44:56.38,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.38,0:44:59.01,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.01,0:45:01.75,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,My heart is pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.75,0:45:05.70,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's the time and emotion you've invested up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.70,0:45:08.20,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's definitely not a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.20,0:45:13.20,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I've always aimed for this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.20,0:45:16.21,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's the stage I've dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.21,0:45:20.71,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Right now, I just want to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.71,0:45:24.25,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I won't say it's okay to be bad or offer any consolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.25,0:45:27.62,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,…I understand what you're trying to say, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.62,0:45:34.13,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll just do my very best and show everyone what I can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.13,0:45:35.13,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Lilja.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.13,0:45:36.22,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.48,0:45:39.45,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.48,0:45:39.45,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Just like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.23,0:45:42.17,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.17,0:45:44.23,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.11,0:45:48.83,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm going to become an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.83,0:45:50.51,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...! Katsuragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.51,0:45:53.30,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Please watch over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.72,0:48:31.89,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,—Katsuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.89,0:48:34.90,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.40,0:48:38.33,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,How did I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.33,0:48:42.85,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I gave it everything I had, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.91,0:48:45.84,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.84,0:48:50.31,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I messed that up, and I messed this up too...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.31,0:48:52.11,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.11,0:48:55.11,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That was an amazing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.11,0:48:58.19,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.19,0:49:02.97,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes. Because everyone in the audience was smiling and having a great time, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.81,0:49:08.71,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Your hard work, Katsuragi, truly touched everyone's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.71,0:49:13.02,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You might have noticed, but she was in the audience too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.44,0:49:16.19,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.19,0:49:18.22,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I saw her from the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.22,0:49:23.58,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Do you think it reached Sumika's heart too?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.58,0:49:27.88,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm sure it reached her. Your singing, Katsuragi, has that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.88,0:49:29.33,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.33,0:49:33.64,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...That being said, it's true there were quite a few mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.64,0:49:36.64,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.64,0:49:38.14,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.14,0:49:40.28,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I guess I'm not cut out to be a producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.28,0:49:42.43,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,W-What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.43,0:49:46.52,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I decided to produce you because I saw your strong determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.52,0:49:53.56,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,However, in reality, I felt that the obstacles standing in your way, Katsuragi, were quite high and challenging.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.34,0:49:57.29,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.29,0:50:01.83,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi, you're an even more amazing idol than I ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.10,0:50:07.90,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.34,0:50:13.50,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done anything on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.50,0:50:19.23,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You've brought me this far, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.23,0:50:25.44,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So, um... really, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.44,0:50:28.58,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.70,0:50:31.71,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,We're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.70,0:50:31.71,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's keep working hard together from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.25,0:50:34.21,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.52,0:50:38.19,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Let's keep working hard together, always!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.19,0:50:42.89,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you from now on, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.73,0:50:50.04,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's make a note of today's production status.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.04,0:50:53.78,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That was a fantastic performance with everyone smiling! She's an amazing idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.90,0:50:58.62,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Oh? Katsuragi? Isn't today supposed to be a day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.62,0:51:01.55,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, hi there, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.33,0:51:06.08,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I just couldn't help myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.08,0:51:10.06,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I just didn't want to lose the feeling from yesterday's live performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.06,0:51:12.97,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I just wanted to practice a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.97,0:51:17.21,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I told you before, overworking isn't good for you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.21,0:51:22.03,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Uh, well, it's just for a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.03,0:51:27.22,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I promise I won't overdo it like last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.22,0:51:30.29,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'll let it slide just for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.22,0:51:30.29,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Well, I guess there's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.77,0:51:34.46,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Really? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.46,0:51:35.84,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm so happy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.84,0:51:40.09,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm always amazed by your enthusiasm, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.09,0:51:43.43,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...The live performance was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.43,0:51:47.60,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I just can't calm down from all the excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.42,0:51:51.79,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want to stand on that stage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.79,0:51:55.33,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Next time, I want to sing even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.98,0:51:57.98,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I want to dance well.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.98,0:52:05.19,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even when I tried to rest, it was all I could think about, and I just couldn't sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.19,0:52:08.69,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, I was practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.69,0:52:13.33,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,If you're practicing with that much enthusiasm, there's no way I could stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.33,0:52:15.79,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Hello! Sorry to intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.79,0:52:17.87,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Is Lilja here?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.87,0:52:20.50,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, Sumika!?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.50,0:52:22.97,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Ah, I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.97,0:52:24.77,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.77,0:52:29.30,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Yesterday, you were asleep when I got back, and by the time I woke up, you were already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.30,0:52:31.64,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.64,0:52:34.40,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,As soon as I got back, I just felt so drained...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.40,0:52:39.06,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,No worries—your performance was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.93,0:52:42.78,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.65,0:52:46.76,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I could see you from the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.76,0:52:48.96,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Really? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.96,0:52:53.77,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,There were so many people in the audience, I'm surprised you managed to spot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.77,0:52:55.66,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.17,0:52:58.99,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I was hoping to find you, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.99,0:53:03.41,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Wow! You like me too much, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.41,0:53:06.18,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,You're making me blush saying things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.18,0:53:12.77,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,If I'm imagining things, it's embarrassing, but towards the end, were you crying a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.77,0:53:16.33,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,...I wasn't crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.33,0:53:19.50,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I mean, I was really moved, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.50,0:53:22.58,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,No, you were definitely crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.58,0:53:24.95,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Don't say unnecessary things!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.95,0:53:27.07,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I just got something in my eye, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.07,0:53:29.04,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Haha...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.98,0:53:33.20,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.20,0:53:36.75,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to my live performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.57,0:53:40.21,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,...I just wanted to see it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.21,0:53:42.59,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,It's nothing to be thanked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.59,0:53:46.22,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm the one who should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.72,0:53:50.22,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,After seeing a performance like that, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.22,0:53:54.01,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I just can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.73,0:53:57.92,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Sumika...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.92,0:54:05.51,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Seeing you spread your wings like that, I thought, "I want to be like that too."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.51,0:54:11.67,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I want to stand next to Lilja and soar even higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.67,0:54:15.85,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I feel the same way... I want that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.85,0:54:17.20,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Sumika...!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.20,0:54:21.61,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about when I went to watch your lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.61,0:54:25.20,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I pretended not to remember our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.20,0:54:28.02,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I actually do remember it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.02,0:54:31.30,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I actually remembered it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.30,0:54:37.46,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,But I just didn't have the courage to try again, so I couldn't say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.27,0:54:43.87,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.07,0:54:49.02,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I believed in you, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.02,0:54:55.21,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Listening to you singing gave me the courage to keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.21,0:54:57.63,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Watching your live performance, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.63,0:55:02.17,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,You're working so hard and giving it your all...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.17,0:55:06.30,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I feel like I need to try even harder too.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.30,0:55:08.96,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,You made me feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.96,0:55:14.61,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone who watched felt the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.81,0:55:21.58,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I'm glad it reached you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.58,0:55:24.31,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm still inexperienced, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.31,0:55:28.54,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,My singing can change someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.54,0:55:32.58,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It reaches the hearts of those I want to touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.58,0:55:36.75,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Yeah, Lilja, you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.75,0:55:39.55,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I knew it from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.12,0:55:44.00,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.28,0:55:49.83,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting me to become an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.83,0:55:53.11,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,If you hadn't been there for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.11,0:55:56.64,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I probably wouldn't have been able to find the courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.64,0:55:59.45,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You were the one who took my hand and led me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.45,0:56:03.13,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,And Senpai gave me that push forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.13,0:56:06.56,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Because of that, I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.56,0:56:10.86,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So when you seemed like you were going to quit,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.86,0:56:14.65,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I thought, "Now it's my turn."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.65,0:56:20.69,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,This time, it's my turn to reach out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.69,0:56:23.40,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Lilja...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.40,0:56:26.83,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hey, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.83,0:56:30.35,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Let's become idols together, the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.35,0:56:32.38,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,...Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.88,0:56:35.84,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Absolutely, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.84,0:56:38.68,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'll catch up to you soon, Lilja.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.68,0:56:40.45,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.45,0:56:43.89,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.42,0:56:48.09,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Sorry for interrupting your lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.73,0:56:51.09,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,That's all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.09,0:56:53.59,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.27,0:56:56.96,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.96,0:56:58.50,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Here's a little treat for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.50,0:57:00.47,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Feel free to have it during your break.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.47,0:57:04.45,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Producer, too. Please have some too if you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.45,0:57:06.29,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.29,0:57:08.49,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.49,0:57:11.06,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,No worries at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.06,0:57:13.13,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Good luck with your practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.13,0:57:16.08,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You too, Sumika! Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.08,0:57:17.85,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.85,0:57:21.14,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,I'm off to my lesson now, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.14,0:57:23.68,Default,清夏,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.29,0:57:29.38,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You've got a really good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.38,0:57:32.27,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.27,0:57:36.55,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll catch up. In the meantime, let's keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.55,0:57:38.74,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.74,0:57:43.18,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll keep working hard, step by step.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.18,0:57:45.61,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's the spirit, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.61,0:57:52.19,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's because you're here to support someone like me that I can keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.19,0:57:56.27,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.81,0:58:00.53,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...for choosing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.53,0:58:03.85,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I didn't even know where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.47,0:58:07.48,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You guided me when I was lost in the darkness—
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.48,0:58:10.88,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You showed me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.98,0:58:15.38,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I saw the light in the direction where you were, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.38,0:58:19.51,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...You're exaggerating. To me, you're the one who's the light, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.51,0:58:23.99,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,All I can do is help you shine even brighter, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.99,0:58:26.89,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Even so, I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.89,0:58:29.97,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm the one who should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.97,0:58:33.48,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You gave us such an amazing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.86,0:58:36.73,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.73,0:58:41.07,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,This isn't the end, you know? Katsuragi, we're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.07,0:58:44.37,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,After all, the goal is to become a top idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.84,0:58:47.02,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.02,0:58:51.19,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,If you're there to support me, then—
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.19,0:58:54.85,Default,リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I will become a top idol!
